{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01PdREkRPqduv9dGRaYXgdKF","type":"tool_result","content":"/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-09-wire-output-mapping-design.md-280-   same step map the same env var. Update validation tests.\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-09-wire-output-mapping-design.md-281-\ndocs/plans/2026-03-09-wire-output-mapping-design.md:282:5. **Wire mapping resolution in host executor** — Read source output, evaluate\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-09-wire-output-mapping-design.md-283-   paths, inject env vars. Update executor tests.\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-09-wire-output-mapping-design.md-284-\n--\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-implementation.md-1345-\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-implementation.md-1346-// fakeExecutor records which steps were executed and returns predetermined results.\ndocs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-implementation.md:1347:type fakeExecutor struct {\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-implementation.md-1348-\tresults map[string]string // stepName -> result\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-implementation.md-1349-\tcalled  []string\n--\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-implementation.md-2180-}\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-implementation.md-2181-\ndocs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-implementation.md:2182:type stepExecutor struct {\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-implementation.md-2183-\tworkDir string\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-implementation.md-2184-\tgeneric *generic.Adapter\n--\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-edge-selection-implementation.md-1017-\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-edge-selection-implementation.md-1018-```go\ndocs/plans/2026-02-20-edge-selection-implementation.md:1019:type fakeExecutor struct {\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-edge-selection-implementation.md-1020-\tmu      sync.Mutex\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-edge-selection-implementation.md-1021-\tresults map[string]string"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_